# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Hero image (optional CDN)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# If set, the homepage hero uses this URL instead of files in /public/images/.
# Use a full HTTPS URL (e.g. from Cloudinary).
#
# Where to upload (free tier):
#   1. Open https://cloudinary.com/users/register_free (or sign in)
#   2. Dashboard → Media Library → Upload
#   3. Open the asset → copy "URL" / Delivery URL (looks like:
#      https://res.cloudinary.com/<your-cloud-name>/image/upload/v1234567/<folder>/<file>.jpg)
#
# Quality: in the URL path, insert transforms after /upload/ — e.g.
#   .../image/upload/q_100,f_auto,w_2400/...
#   q_100 = minimal compression; f_auto = AVIF/WebP where supported by their delivery
#
# Then paste that full URL below and restart `npm run dev`.
#
NEXT_PUBLIC_HERO_IMAGE_URL=
